    "There have been multiple attempts since to improve upon the original formulation.",
    "Liu and Li (2012) presents one of the most objective frameworks in this thread.",
    "Their framework is intentionally broad and builds upon the rich literature on task complexity, task difficulty, and cognitive load.",
    "We leverage this framework for defining and measuring task complexity in our work.",
    "The framework presented in (Liu and Li, 2012) defines ten complexity dimensions that can be used to measure the complexities of a set of tasks."
